s/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定係用華為既公司先中到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"尋晚見有師兄話數碼通x愛立信係首間展示5G技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"現實係殘酷的，已經打定輸數 smt 冇份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70af627ac46cb605c294d88bb71bf667a5f89934","tid":940366,"uid":1874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"CSL就算拎到5G又點？<br />\n到時地鐵照load空氣，識飛都無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}